# OutlineSubgroupChildren

**Structure**

A type-erased view representing the children in an outline subgroup.

## Declaration

```swift
struct OutlineSubgroupChildren
```

## Overview

[doc://com.apple.SwiftUI/documentation/SwiftUI/OutlineGroup] uses this type as a generic constraint for the `Content` of the [doc://com.apple.SwiftUI/documentation/SwiftUI/DisclosureGroup] instances it creates.

- View
